title: Mini Ep 14: MTG(ee Thanks) Cribs with Jackie J.
itunes:title: Mini Ep 14: MTG(ee Thanks) Cribs with Jackie J.
itunes:subtitle: Getting ready for Baby Natch means Jackie's shopping.
description:
We’re baaaack with another mini episode. Jackie is Big Pregnant right now which means she’s Natch Nesting! Buying cribs, taking a real Woo Woo baby class (Caroline is doing judgey eyes), and more. Make sure you catch this week’s Natch mini…it might explain some of the jokes you hear on this mini.


Mentioned on this episode:


  • Hotel Lobby Candle: https://rstyle.me/+4uFoDvwuW0cMB1U-gpvl2Q 
  • The Packing Cubes: https://amzn.to/36ll27X 
  • The Cord Organizer: https://amzn.to/3KIC3rN 
  • The Facebook group! https://www.facebook.com/groups/geethanks 


Shop our Amazon Storefront: https://www.amazon.com/shop/geethanksjustboughtit
